data.description: A blend of modern living & a touch of countryside charm.This charming Modern Farmhouse is ready for horses & dog boarding business. Newly remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 bath modern farmhouse blends classic charm, contemporary aesthetics. The kitchen is equipped with new black stainless SMART appliances,a multitude of cabinets & 8 lazy susan turn tables plus corian countertops. The 2-stall horse barn has attached storage & fenced paddock will surely cater to the needs of your hay eating friends. The 6' high black chain link-cedar fenced dog park, complete with agility equipment, adjoins a temperature controlled 10 bay indoor & 10 bay outdoor dog kennel, providing the ultimate comfort for your furry friends or opens the door to a future dog boarding business. Mature trees enhance the serene ambiance. Newly paved driveway - parking area. The 90' well allows for watering landscaping & animals. Fiber optic high speed internet available.Don't miss out on this exceptional home & business opportunity.
